title: [SNES] More Super Mario Kart - 25th Anniversary Hack
description:
-=More Super Mario Kart-=
***A Super Mario Kart Hack by LHP***

A celebration of 25 years of Mario Kart, made with love!

ROM is already patched and has been tested with Snes9x and ZSNES.

[FEATURES]
-20 newly designed courses in the spirit of the original game.
-Slight graphical modifications. 

Enjoy!
